metadata.name: VOICE आवाज़
metadata.description:
In this artwork, I am reflecting myself. I was stuck in a place where people were classic and well-worn. These people keep their neck high by keeping their success and their good lives, so they don't have the ability to understand others' difficulties. Therefore, he doesn't like to speak with those below his class.


Pen-Ink on paper 
22 x 30 cm
